Install Repos on Termux (get from Google Play store)

 apt-get install root-repo -y
 apt-get install unstable-repo -y
 apt-get install x11-repo -y
 
 All in one command:
 apt-get install root-repo -y && apt-get install unstable-repo -y && apt-get install x11-repo -y
 
 (Doing apt-get or just typing apt uses less Megabytes than pkg)
 
 Install Repos on Linux (crostini, ubuntu, debian)
 
 sudo apt install root-repo -y 
 sudo apt install unstable-repo -y
 sudo apt install x11-repo
 
 All in one command:
 sudo apt install root-repo -y && sudo apt install unstable-repo -y && sudo apt install x11-repo
 

 
